###Get the service document
http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/CatalogService

###Get the service document metadata
http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/CatalogService/$metadata

###Get All Employees data
http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/CatalogService/EmployeeSet

###Get Employee data by ID
http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/CatalogService/EmployeeSet/02BD2137-0890-1EEA-A6C2-BB55C19887FB

###Get Employees data based on pagination
http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/CatalogService/EmployeeSet?$top=2&skip=2

###Get Employees data based on filter
http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/CatalogService/EmployeeSet?$filter=sex eq 'F'

###Count the employees
http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/CatalogService/EmployeeSet/$count

###Selection of few columns
http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/CatalogService/EmployeeSet?$select=ID,nameFirst,sex

###Insert Employee Data
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/CatalogService/EmployeeSet
Content-Type: application/json

{

      "nameFirst": "Aashish",
      "nameMiddle": null,
      "nameLast": "Kumar",
      "nameInitials": null,
      "sex": "M",
      "language": "E",
      "phoneNumber": "+91 7015679376",
      "email": "aashish122001@gmail.com",
      "loginName": "STYLES",
      "Currency_code": "USD",
      "salaryAmount": 1000000,
      "accountNumber": "12039483020",
      "bankId": "510000655",
      "bankName": "My Bank of India"
    }

###Get the newly created Employee
http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/CatalogService/EmployeeSet/6f2be9b8-4e7d-4e65-ad8a-d32bf98839c4

####Update Employee Data
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/CatalogService/EmployeeSet/a27497c1-814a-4323-801e-c890cf860475
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "salaryAmount":"2000000",
    "Currency_code":"EUR"
}

###Delete Employee Data
DELETE http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/CatalogService/EmployeeSet/6f2be9b8-4e7d-4e65-ad8a-d32bf98839c4

###Get all Purchase orders
http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/CatalogService/POs

###Get Single Purchase order
http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/CatalogService/POs/74867AD200E41EDBA5D8B0C98DC34052

###Get the PO and PO Items together - using $expand
http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/CatalogService/POs/74867AD200E41EDBA5D8B0C98DC2E052?$expand=Items

###Boosting a order
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/CatalogService/POs('74867AD200E41EDBA5D8B0C98DC34052')/CatalogService.boost
Content-Type: application/json

{
    
}
###Test function to get the largest order
http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/CatalogService/largestOrder()

